title: Prop-005, Trader Joe Farm Swap!
body:
This new proposal aims at adjusting expired partnered staking Farms and introducing a Farm Swap with TraderJoe!

One thing some may notice is the changes result in a net 0.1x weight gain resulting in a positive APR gain across ALL farms.

Our new Farm introduced in this proposal is FTM-JOE with a weight of 0.5x. JOE is the token of TraderJoe, the largest DEX on Avalanche and this signals a cross chain farm swap between our two protocols! If this new Farm is implemented, Trader Joe will introduce a stake AVAX-BOO Joe LP earn JOE farm on avalanche! In addition, both BOO and JOE will be added to the SpookySwap bridge on the Fantom <> Avalanche route.

Finally, the https://retreeb.io/ team will be refilling the xBOO TREEB pool to continue partnered staking!

|    Farm   | Weight (old) | Weight (new) |
|:---------:|:------------:|:------------:|
| FTM-SHADE |       0.4      |      0     |
|  FTM-TREEB |       0.8      |      0.6    |

|    New Farm   | Weight | 
|:---------:|:------------:|
|  FTM-JOE  |       0.5      |
